Package: imphash
Version: 1.1.2
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-4-1 (>= 4.12), libadwaita-1-0 (>= 1.5), libgdk-pixbuf-2.0-0, libglib2.0-0, libc6
Maintainer: antoxa78 <antoxa78@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/antoxa78/ImpHash
Description: Perceptual image hash comparison tool
 ImpHash is a GTK4/libadwaita GUI application that finds similar
 images using perceptual hashing (dHash). It scans directories,
 computes image hashes, groups similar images, and helps you
 review and deduplicate them.
